            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Some translations are done in deeply nested calls:\r\n```c\r\nstatic char *illegal_char(char *errbuf, size_t errbuflen, int c)\r\n{\r\n  if (errbuf == NULL) {\r\n    return \"\";\r\n  }\r\n  vim_snprintf(errbuf, errbuflen, _(\"E539: Illegal character <%s>\"),\r\n               (char *)transchar(c));\r\n  return errbuf;\r\n}\r\n```\r\nso preventing translation may make the code more ugly.",
