            "body": "> so preventing translation may make the code more ugly.\r\n\r\nok, let's do whatever results in simpler code.\r\n\r\nI guess I was thinking we could modify `_()` to check if the current context is an RPC/API function, and skip translation.\r\n\r\nTranslating actually has a non-trivial performance cost, so there's that.",
